metadata.name: Blue Eyes #1
metadata.description:
Blue Eyed Sam, 2021.

This is a new take from my series 'Hoodies and Blue Eyes', presented at [Fotomuseum Winterthur](https://www.fotomuseum.ch/en/) in 2019.

Other of my features include [Vogue Italy](https://www.vogue.it/fotografia/gallery/judy-by-karla-hiraldo-voleau),  [It's Nice That](https://www.itsnicethat.com/articles/karla-voleau-hola-mi-amoi-photography-230818), [I-D](https://i-d.vice.com/en_uk/article/5dm3za/20-photographers-follow-on-instagram-colour), or [W Magazine](https://www.wmagazine.com/fashion/dior-maria-grazia-chiuri-rachele-regini-interview-2021).
